title: SOUTH  OF  HAVEN,  WEST  OF  HELL  (2000)
description:
RELEASE DATE : JANUARY 28th, 2000


DRAMA / WESTERN


Valentine Casey is a Marshal in the desolate Tucson territory of the early 1900's. On Christmas Eve, his outlaw family pays him a disturbing visit. He must confront the sins of his past. He and his partner, U.S. Christmas, journey through the desert to a small town that the ruthless Henry Clan has hit in order to save Casey's love, Adelyne.  Written by Sujit R. Varma
